BANC connectome data
--------------------

banc_888_edgelist_simple_v2.feather and banc_888_meta.feather are not
distributed here (347MB, and not this project's to license). setup.sh downloads
them from the Lee Lab's public bucket and verifies them by size and sha256:

    https://storage.googleapis.com/lee-lab_brain-and-nerve-cord-fly-connectome/compiled_data/banc_888/

The dataset itself is at https://doi.org/10.7910/DVN/8TFGGB, released under
CC BY 4.0 (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0), and described in
Bates, Phelps, Kim, Yang et al., Nature (2026),
https://doi.org/10.1038/s41586-026-10735-w. Cite them, not this repository, for
the data.


